    "data": [
        {
            "title": "歐協聯 | 安東尼近況極勇  貝迪斯受讓平半「客」穩",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"前曼聯球員安東尼馬菲奧斯不但擅長策動快速反擊，更有極出色的破門能力。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3c43ef631adb919e11f840bb149c7af3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050817513235463.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">前曼聯球員安東尼馬菲奧斯不但擅長策動快速反擊，更有極出色的破門能力。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>貝迪斯在歐協聯4強首回合中對費倫天拿時佔著優勢，並以2:1佔先，今晚次回合時可伺機而動，佔盡戰術優勢，前曼聯球員安東尼馬菲奧斯不但擅長策動快速反擊，更有極出色的破門能力，連場取得入球，有其壓陣貝迪斯可保持4連勝強勢，受讓平手半球「客勝」極穩。<strong>（beIN SPORTS CONNECT周五凌晨3:00直播）</strong>\n</p>\n<p>近況極勇的貝迪斯在上場聯賽有安東尼的絕殺世界波，最終以2:1反勝愛斯賓奴，在各項賽事已保持4連勝佳績，這名巴西翼鋒亦在這4場賽事中射入3球，難怪名宿祖亞昆賽後笑言願意出動自己的私家車「綁架」安東尼，將其留低在貝迪斯，此子同樣在首回合中對紫百合的賽事中射入奠勝球，今場作客之下，有其策動反擊，戰術優勢更大。紫百合近期在巴西右翼衛杜杜受傷後，進攻方面明顯受到影響，已連續兩場未能射入多於1球兼錄得2連敗，今場仍只能以左腳仔柏列斯客串，貝迪斯受讓更筍，大有機會波盤齊贏。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067935/即時-體育-歐協聯-安東尼近況極勇-貝迪斯受讓平半-客-穩",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:56:23",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐霸盃 | 熱刺小勝波杜基林特「和」味",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"熱刺今場作客波杜基林特賠率有分頭。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/444858b4f75936b08d4e6e713516fe0d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050817505978213.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">熱刺今場作客波杜基林特賠率有分頭。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>波杜基林特在歐霸盃首回合對熱刺時，幾乎無法創造任何具威脅埋門，唯其的主場戰績極佳，導致熱刺今場作客挪威賠率顯得更有分頭，熱刺中場賓坦古在首回合中作出多次攔截，絕對是今場能否頂住對方狂攻的重要人物，只要發揮正常，熱刺有力小勝而回，讓球主客和主隊受讓一球「和」有逾4倍分頭值得冷敲。<strong>（Now 638台周五凌晨3:00直播） </strong>\n</p>\n<p>波杜基林特的高位防線和迫搶戰術，跟熱刺領隊主帥普斯迪高古以往的套路如出一轍，普帥在首回合中的部署，就如面對熱刺以往的缺點一樣，刻意採用更多長傳和高波，破解對手高位防線，從而收到極佳的效果，尤其在2:0的入球中，占士麥迪臣從後殺上，接應柏度保路的長傳破門可見一斑。今場作客挪威，在部署上亦只大同小異，只要在防守上能成功抵抗對手，單靠長傳反擊已足以贏波晉級。\n\n</p>\n<p>在今仗次回合，熱刺面對的唯一分別，只在於波杜基林特在今屆賽事於仿真草的主場表現極佳，近5次作東更全勝，能否成功抗衡波杜基林特的高運動量打法是今場關鍵。 在首回合中，防守中場賓坦古成為熱刺致勝基石，此子在中場造出全場最多的4次成功攔截，12次個人對抗中贏了11次，是球隊能在首回合贏波的無名英雄，由其領導的中場大有機會能完成破壞和掃蕩的任務。\n\n</p>\n<p>熱刺前場人手短缺，孫興民和占士麥迪臣因傷缺陣，其餘戰將狀態未算出色，實在未有大勝條件，唯小勝機會不低，博其贏一球有逾4倍分頭。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067934/即時-體育-歐霸盃-熱刺小勝波杜基林特-和-味",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:56:24",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "元朗私家車失控剷上山坡 司機送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fff101af790e89149c285a681435ac2d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050817503233042.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（8日）午4時許，一輛白色私家車沿朗天路行駛，駛至唐人新村交匯處支路時，失控撞向水馬，剷入路邊草叢，車身傾斜擱於水馬和草叢之間，男司機報稱手部受傷，由救護車送院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237386/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/072e04c9c3b7a9bf1e401942a219151f/2025-05/02_1_8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4237387/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dcda8058aa24a92ab3269c1338d51756/2025-05/03_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車剷上山坡上。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067933/即時-港聞-元朗私家車失控剷上山坡-司機送院",
